Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: 445 South Street in Morristown offers immediate access to I-287 and is in close proximity to the primary commuting corridors of I-78, I-80, Routes 10 and 24. Newark Liberty International Airport is just 18 miles from the property.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: 445 South Street is a 320,274 RSF, 4-story premier Class A office building. Originally constructed in 1982, the building was renovated in 2008. Facility offers 4/1,000 SF parking, food service and fitness center.
